data.description: Live the dream on this large 78.2 acre farm.  Enjoy open pastures, multiple ponds, and an outstanding view throughout. Charming farmhouse renovated in 1994 with over 3400 square feet 3 bedrooms and 3 full baths. Large family room with vaulted ceilings and masonry fireplace. Eat-in kitchen and formal dining and living room. Has large master suite with garden tub, separate shower, and double vanities. Large rocking chair front porch and two level deck on back overlooking pasture and ponds. Home has 2 car garage and 23 x 24 walk in crawl space for storage. 41 x 26 barn with stalls and storage rooms and 71 x 100 metal building would be great for shop or hay barn with shelter.
